DriveTrain:

	Teleop Drive
	
	Autonomous Motion: (I method using ENUM to Switch between, using selector between IMU and Encoder)

		setTarget (Handle Turn and Move), set maxSpeed, set direction --> one method --> setAutoParameters

		setGamepad
	
		Spline

			Encoder + PID

		Strafe (4 Directions):

			Encoder + PID

		Turn (2 Directions):

			IMU.Calculate Error + PID

IMU:

	Calculate Error

Robot

	Overloaded Constructor:

		Autonomous: (No Gamepad)

			Drivetrain (Auto) Create Override Run for the Moving Methods

			Auto.setParameters //Default = 0,0,FORWARD


		TeleOp: (Gamepad):

			Drivetrain (TeleOp) Create Override Run for the Teleop Method
			TeleOp.setGamepad(Gamepad)

Auto

	Robot robot = new Robot(No Gamepad)

	Thread drive = new Thread(Robot.Drivetrain (Autonomous))

	setParameters(Whatever is needed)

	drive.run()
	drive.stop()/drive.interupt

	Repeat

TeleOp

	Robot robot = new Robot(Gamepad)

	Thread drive = new Thread(Robot.Drivetrain (TeleOp))

	while (opModeIsActive) {
		drive.start();
	}
